description: Fully renovated two-family home in the heart of South Boston! This property features brand new siding, central A/C and mini splits, hardwood floors, spacious bedrooms, and modern kitchens and bathrooms with stainless steel appliances. Enjoy a large patio space in the rear, perfect for outdoor entertaining. Unit 1 is a large, renovated 1-bedroom unit currently collecting $3,300 a month in rent. Upstairs, you'll find a spacious duplex with 4 bedrooms plus an office, collecting $5,700 a month in rent. There's also potential to add value by converting the basement to a duplex for Unit 1. Additionally, there is room to increase the rent roll after the current lease cycle ends. Low maintenance and ready for new owners to enjoy. The location is fantastic—within walking distance to Broadway shops and restaurants, and next to Thomas Park. Don't miss this incredible opportunity!
